sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant AccountConsultController
    participant ConsultAccountService
    participant AccountRepository
    participant LedgerEntryRepository
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Client->>AccountConsultController: GET /api/v1/accounts/{id}/balance (X-Customer-Id)
    AccountConsultController->>ConsultAccountService: getBalance(accountId, customerId)
    ConsultAccountService->>AccountRepository: findById(accountId)
    AccountRepository->>DB: SELECT account
    AccountRepository-->>ConsultAccountService: Account
    ConsultAccountService->>ConsultAccountService: Vérifier ownership
    ConsultAccountService-->>AccountConsultController: balanceCents
    AccountConsultController-->>Client: 200 + BalanceResponse

    Note over Client,DB: Pour l'historique (ledger):
    Client->>AccountConsultController: GET /api/v1/accounts/{id}/ledger
    AccountConsultController->>ConsultAccountService: getHistory(accountId, customerId)
    ConsultAccountService->>LedgerEntryRepository: findByAccountIdOrderByCreatedAtDesc
    LedgerEntryRepository->>DB: SELECT ledger_entries
    LedgerEntryRepository-->>ConsultAccountService: Page<LedgerEntry>
    ConsultAccountService-->>AccountConsultController: Page
    AccountConsultController-->>Client: 200 + LedgerPageResponse
